---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import snap from '../data/track_snapshot.json';

// Build-time offline fallback (auto-generated by scripts/generate_track_snapshot.py
// from data/golive_status.json + data/equity_curve_daily.json — never hand-edited).
// The inline script below overrides this live from /api/v1/golive on any real visit.
const realDays = snap.real_track_days != null ? snap.real_track_days : '—';  // ONE source, no hardcode (FIX-2)
---

<Layout
  title="Methodology &amp; Evidence — SPA earn-defi.com"
  description="Methodology and evidence journal for SPA. Current status, live data links, protocol whitelist, audit status, and documentation."
  canonical="https://earn-defi.com/due-diligence"
>

  <!-- Nav -->
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-xs text-accent-400 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" data-ru="Слой доказательств">Proof Layer</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-ru="Методология и доказательства">Methodology &amp; Evidence</h1>
      <p class="text-white/50 text-lg leading-relaxed" data-ru="Методология и журнал доказательств для SPA.">
        Methodology and evidence journal for SPA.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Current Status -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-border" data-ru="Текущий статус">Current Status</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-xs text-white/50 font-mono mb-1" data-ru="Режим">Mode</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-warn font-medium" data-ru="Paper trading">Paper Trading</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-xs text-white/50 font-mono mb-1" data-ru="Капитал">Capital</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/70 font-medium">$100k USDC</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-xs text-white/50 font-mono mb-1" data-ru="Старт">Start</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/70 font-medium" data-ru="22 июня 2026">Jun 22, 2026</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-xs text-white/50 font-mono mb-1">Go-Live</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/70 font-medium" data-ru="~21 июля 2026">~Jul 21, 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-4 rounded-lg border border-ok-border bg-ok-bg p-4 flex items-center justify-between">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/70">GoLiveChecker</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/55" data-ru="Автоматические критерии готовности">Automated readiness criteria</p>
        </div>
        <span class="text-sm font-mono text-ok" data-ru={`${snap.gates_passed}/${snap.gates_total} пройдено (НЕ ГОТОВО)`}>{snap.gates_passed}/{snap.gates_total} passing (NOT READY)</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Verify us yourself (Q2-8) — the full "don't trust us, check us" chain, no manual ask -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-border" data-ru="Проверьте нас сами">Verify Us Yourself</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-5" data-ru="Не верьте нам на слово. Два детерминированных, zero-dependency скрипта воспроизводят всё, что мы публикуем — на нашем публичном data/. Exit 0 или скрипт называет точную сломанную строку.">
        Don't take our word for anything. Two deterministic, zero-dependency scripts reproduce everything we publish, from our public <code>data/</code>. Exit 0 — or the script names the exact broken row.
      </p>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-5 mb-4">
        <p class="text-xs text-accent-400 font-mono uppercase tracking-wider mb-2" data-ru="1. Цепочка доказательств цела">1 · Proof chain is intact</p>
        <pre class="text-xs font-mono text-white/70 overflow-x-auto mb-2">python3 scripts/verify_spa.py data/</pre>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/55 leading-relaxed" data-ru="Покрывает все 7 поверхностей: decision-chain, exit-NAV, anchors, equity-track, tournament, RWA-NAV, sleeves. Точный --expect-head и SHA-256 самого верификатора — в живом DD-паке (auto-generated, guarded).">Covers all 7 surfaces — decision chain, exit-NAV, anchors, equity track, tournament, RWA-NAV, sleeves. The exact <code>--expect-head</code> fingerprint and the verifier's own SHA-256 live in the auto-generated, test-guarded DD pack (<code>docs/DD_PACK.md</code>).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-5 mb-4">
        <p class="text-xs text-accent-400 font-mono uppercase tracking-wider mb-2" data-ru="2. Защиты доказуемо срабатывают">2 · The safety machinery FIRES</p>
        <pre class="text-xs font-mono text-white/70 overflow-x-auto mb-2">python3 scripts/defenses_exercised_report.py</pre>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/55 leading-relaxed" data-ru="11/11 защит срабатывают через тот же governance-код, что и дневной цикл: two-tier kill (SOFT −5% / HARD −10%), soft-derisk блокирует любые NEW/INCREASE. Кривая монотонна (0% просадки) — тормоза спят, потому что не штормило, а не потому что их нет.">11/11 defenses fire through the <b>same</b> governance code the daily cycle uses: two-tier kill ladder (SOFT −5% de-risk / HARD −10% all-cash), soft de-risk blocks every NEW position and INCREASE. The live curve is monotonic (0% drawdown) — the brakes are dormant because it never stressed, not because they're absent.</p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-white/55 leading-relaxed" data-ru="Живые публичные поверхности:">Live public surfaces:
        <a href="/readiness" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">/readiness</a> ·
        <a href="/refusals" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">/refusals</a> ·
        <a href="/exit-nav" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">/exit-nav</a> ·
        <a href="/proof-of-reserves" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">/proof-of-reserves</a> ·
        <a href="/track-record" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">/track-record</a> ·
        <a href="/fundability" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">/fundability</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Strategy Status -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-border" data-ru="Статус стратегий">Strategy Status</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border-strong">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-border-strong bg-bg-surface">
              <th class="text-left text-white/55 font-mono text-xs p-3" data-ru="Стратегия">Strategy</th>
              <th class="text-left text-white/55 font-mono text-xs p-3" data-ru="Статус">Status</th>
              <th class="text-left text-white/55 font-mono text-xs p-3" data-ru="Paper-трекинг">Paper Tracking</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-white/55">
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <td class="p-3 text-white/70 font-medium">Core</td>
              <td class="p-3"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-ok bg-ok-bg px-2 py-0.5 rounded" data-ru="На paper-трекинге">Paper tracked</span></td>
              <td class="p-3 text-white/60" data-ru="С 22 июня 2026 (evidenced anchor)">Since Jun 22, 2026 (evidenced anchor)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <td class="p-3 text-white/70 font-medium">Preserve</td>
              <td class="p-3"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-white/55 bg-bg-surface-2 px-2 py-0.5 rounded" data-ru="Целевой профиль">Target profile</span></td>
              <td class="p-3 text-white/55" data-ru="Запланировано">Planned</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-3 text-white/70 font-medium">Max Yield</td>
              <td class="p-3"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-white/55 bg-bg-surface-2 px-2 py-0.5 rounded" data-ru="Целевой профиль">Target profile</span></td>
              <td class="p-3 text-white/55" data-ru="Запланировано">Planned</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Live Data Links -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-border" data-ru="Ссылки на живые данные">Live Data Links</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/#live-stats" class="rounded-xl border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-5 hover:border-ok-border transition-colors group">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/80 group-hover:text-white mb-1" data-ru="Дашборд">Dashboard</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/55" data-ru="Живые paper-метрики: дни трека, APY, Sharpe, просадка">Live paper metrics: Track Days, APY, Sharpe, Drawdown</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/#live-stats" class="rounded-xl border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-5 hover:border-ok-border transition-colors group">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/80 group-hover:text-white mb-1" data-ru="Блокировки риска">Risk Blocks</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/55" data-ru="Все заблокированные ребалансировки залогированы и с временными метками">All blocked rebalances logged and timestamped</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/#live-stats" class="rounded-xl border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-5 hover:border-ok-border transition-colors group">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/80 group-hover:text-white mb-1" data-ru="Логи сделок">Trade Logs</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/55" data-ru="Каждый цикл залогирован с обоснованием">Every cycle logged with reasoning</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/#live-stats" class="rounded-xl border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-5 hover:border-ok-border transition-colors group">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/80 group-hover:text-white mb-1">GoLiveChecker</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/55" data-ru={`${snap.gates_passed}/${snap.gates_total} критериев пройдено (НЕ ГОТОВО) — готовность в реальном времени`}>{snap.gates_passed}/{snap.gates_total} criteria passing (NOT READY) — real-time readiness</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Documentation -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-border" data-ru="Документация">Documentation</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <a href="/trust" class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-4 hover:border-ok-border transition-colors group">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80 group-hover:text-white" data-ru="Архитектура доверия">Trust Architecture</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/55" data-ru="Модель контроля, кастоди, 9 ключевых вопросов">Control model, custody, 9 key questions</p>
          </div>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-white/20 group-hover:text-ok">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/risk" class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-4 hover:border-ok-border transition-colors group">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80 group-hover:text-white" data-ru="Риск">Risk</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/55" data-ru="Категории, матрица, стресс-сценарии">Categories, matrix, stress scenarios</p>
          </div>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-white/20 group-hover:text-ok">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/risk-disclosure" class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-4 hover:border-ok-border transition-colors group">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80 group-hover:text-white" data-ru="Раскрытие рисков">Risk Disclosure</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/55" data-ru="Полное юридическое раскрытие">Full legal disclosure</p>
          </div>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-white/20 group-hover:text-ok">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/security" class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-surface p-4 group hover:border-ok/40 transition-colors">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70" data-ru="Базовая безопасность">Security Baseline</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/55" data-ru="Security-обзор + pre-live чеклист">Security review + pre-live checklist</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-white/20 group-hover:text-ok" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/emergency-withdrawal" class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-surface p-4 group hover:border-ok/40 transition-colors">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70" data-ru="Экстренный вывод">Emergency Withdrawal</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/55" data-ru="Путь экстренного вывода + kill-switch">Emergency-withdrawal path + kill-switch ladder</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-white/20 group-hover:text-ok" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Protocol Whitelist -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-border" data-ru="Вайтлист протоколов">Protocol Whitelist</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border-strong">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-border-strong bg-bg-surface">
              <th class="text-left text-white/55 font-mono text-xs p-3" data-ru="Протокол">Protocol</th>
              <th class="text-left text-white/55 font-mono text-xs p-3" data-ru="Уровень">Tier</th>
              <th class="text-left text-white/55 font-mono text-xs p-3" data-ru="Сеть">Chain</th>
              <th class="text-left text-white/55 font-mono text-xs p-3">TVL</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-white/55">
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <td class="p-3 text-white/70">Aave V3</td>
              <td class="p-3"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-ok">Tier 1</span></td>
              <td class="p-3">Ethereum</td>
              <td class="p-3">$15B+</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <td class="p-3 text-white/70">Compound V3</td>
              <td class="p-3"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-ok">Tier 1</span></td>
              <td class="p-3">Ethereum</td>
              <td class="p-3">$3B+</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <td class="p-3 text-white/70">Morpho Blue</td>
              <td class="p-3"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-ok">Tier 1</span></td>
              <td class="p-3">Ethereum</td>
              <td class="p-3">$4B+</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <td class="p-3 text-white/70">Spark</td>
              <td class="p-3"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-ok">Tier 1</span></td>
              <td class="p-3">Ethereum</td>
              <td class="p-3">$5B+</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <td class="p-3 text-white/70">Sky/sUSDS</td>
              <td class="p-3"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-ok">Tier 1</span> <span class="text-xs text-white/50" data-ru="(условно)">(conditional)</span></td>
              <td class="p-3">Ethereum</td>
              <td class="p-3">$8B+</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <td class="p-3 text-white/70">Yearn V3</td>
              <td class="p-3"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-warn">Tier 2</span></td>
              <td class="p-3">Ethereum</td>
              <td class="p-3">$500M+</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <td class="p-3 text-white/70">Euler V2</td>
              <td class="p-3"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-warn">Tier 2</span></td>
              <td class="p-3">Ethereum</td>
              <td class="p-3">$500M+</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-border">
              <td class="p-3 text-white/70">Aave V3</td>
              <td class="p-3"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-warn">Tier 2</span></td>
              <td class="p-3">Base</td>
              <td class="p-3">$2B+</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-3 text-white/70">Morpho Blue</td>
              <td class="p-3"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-warn">Tier 2</span></td>
              <td class="p-3">Base</td>
              <td class="p-3">$500M+</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Audit & Review Status -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-border" data-ru="Статус аудита и ревью">Audit &amp; Review Status</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-lg border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-4">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-white/20"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70" data-ru="Аудиты смарт-контрактов">Smart contract audits</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/55" data-ru="Пока неприменимо (этап paper trading, нет live-контрактов)">Not yet applicable (paper trading phase, no live contracts)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-lg border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-4">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-ok"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70" data-ru="Ревью кода">Code review</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/55" data-ru="Внутреннее ревью завершено">Internal review complete</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-lg border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-4">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-warn"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70" data-ru="Внешний аудит">External audit</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/55" data-ru="Запланирован перед go-live">Planned before go-live</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-lg border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-4">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-warn"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70" data-ru="Bug bounty">Bug bounty</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/55" data-ru="Пока не активна — запланирована к go-live">Not yet active &mdash; planned for go-live</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Backtest Methodology -->
    <section id="backtest-methodology" class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-border" data-ru="Методология бэктеста и стандарт доказательств">Backtest Methodology &amp; Evidence Standard</h2>

      <!-- Point-in-Time Standard -->
      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white/80 mb-3" data-ru="Стандарт point-in-time бэктеста">Point-in-Time Backtest Standard</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-4" data-ru="Мы проводим бэктесты по методологии Capital Preservation Algorithm (CPA), которая обеспечивает строгую point-in-time целостность данных.">
          We run our backtests using the Capital Preservation Algorithm (CPA) methodology,
          which enforces strict point-in-time data integrity.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-border-strong bg-bg-surface p-4">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-white/80 mb-1" data-ru="Без look-ahead bias">No Look-Ahead Bias</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/45 leading-relaxed" data-ru="Исторические симуляции используют только протоколы и данные, существовавшие на дату симуляции. Протокол, запущенный в 2023 году, не может появиться в данных бэктеста 2022 года — даже если его данные APY доступны сегодня.">
              Historical simulations only use protocols and data that existed on the simulation date.
              A protocol launched in 2023 cannot appear in 2022 backtest data — even if its APY
              data is available today.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Four-Stage Gate -->
      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white/80 mb-3" data-ru="Четырёхэтапный гейт доказательств">Four-Stage Evidence Gate</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-4" data-ru="Прежде чем будет задействован любой капитал, наши стратегии проходят четыре этапа валидации:">
          Before any capital is deployed, our strategies pass through four validation stages:
        </p>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border-strong">
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-border-strong bg-bg-surface">
                <th class="text-left text-white/55 font-mono text-xs p-3" data-ru="Этап">Stage</th>
